snippet.title: What's New in WoW Classic Season of Discovery | Featuring PlatinumWoW
snippet.description:
New Level Caps, New Quests, New Monsters, New PvP Activities, New End-Game Content, and New Role-Defining Abilities! Join PlatinumWoW for a glimpse into what you can expect to find in WoW Classic Season of Discovery. Live November 30th!

► Dive deeper into Season of Discovery with the Developers https://blizz.ly/47Rt2rU
